{"tid":1295460,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好心啲死廢佬收下把口啦屌","createTime":"2019-07-08T04:37:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T04:56:54.000Z","uid":208606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8eff468f695394aa388fdce5b269212c4976ad91","tid":1295460,"uid":208606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:37:24.000Z","msg":"永久擺食慈雲山明記粉麵。我屌你老母閪，我食緊野隔離枱有條廢佬係度話而家啲後生仔學人去示威，on99咁係度話自己中國人唔明點解啲人會話反共產黨。跟住又係度話跳樓死撚左個啲人係底撚死唔死都無用，仲話佢地收左安家費先會去跳做宣傳，我屌你老母有冇撚人會用自己條命去做宣傳呀仆你個臭街，用下你個傻閪中國翻版腦諗下啦死廢老，話啲人咁撚唔中意中國咪去英國。心諗屌你咩你咁撚中意中國你留係香港做乜撚野<br />\n<br />\n慈雲山明記入面啲職員都係屌鳩啲後生仔無腦亂衝收錢"},{"pid":"72d41ff356b20f90197e9ca3668c2fed069f5bb2","tid":1295460,"uid":208606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:37:53.000Z","msg":"罷*"},{"pid":"445f57994dda3b0f5ee5d09cdc34bac492233529","tid":1295460,"uid":3302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:38:19.000Z","msg":"D死廢老都擺唔得耐<br />\n咪又係一兩年命<br />\n時間一定係企係我地呢面<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c08aff20ca887bd4e80765c61e88241b56d87aef","tid":1295460,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:53:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/Eb8X9uH.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEb8X9uH.gif&h=373fe2eb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f044182a35481db8bfa05824b75fe402da2312ff","tid":1295460,"uid":57339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:56:54.000Z","msg":"呢間垃圾好撚污糟 狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}